  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Mugen Clan, level 4+ <br />Your mastery of your Clan Techniques has evolved, allowing you to manipulate your own chakra reserves once. This evolution in skill grants you the following <br />benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Increase your Constitution or Intelligence ability score <br />by 1, up the maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>Your chakra point maximum increases by an amount equal to your level when you gain this feat. <br />Whenever you gain a level thereafter, your <br />chakra points maximum increases by an additional 1 chakra points.</p></li><li>You can spend an additional 5 chakra when you cast a Mugen Clan Jutsu to roll an additional die from your <strong>Infinity</strong> clan feature and add it to the temporary hit points gained. This can only trigger once per turn.</li></ul>",
